00:00:33,207 --> 00:00:34,686
Jessa Rinaldi,
you're under arrest.

16
00:00:34,730 --> 00:00:37,689
- Any and all fallout
lands on me.

17
00:00:37,733 --> 00:00:41,041
- Believe me, Sharon,
there will be fallout.

18
00:00:43,217 --> 00:00:44,522
- There she is.

19
00:00:44,566 --> 00:00:46,220
- Sharon Goodwin.

20
00:00:46,263 --> 00:00:48,004
Dr. Matthew Cooper
