00:00:51,573 --> 00:00:53,357
- That it was the work
of their rep, Jessa Rinaldi.

24
00:00:53,401 --> 00:00:54,837
Government even have a case?

25
00:00:54,880 --> 00:00:56,186
- Listen, I have no comment.

26
00:00:56,230 --> 00:00:58,406
